category: Devel Libs
requires: cygwin libgfileio0
external-source: libgfileio
sdesc: "C++ library that wraps around the standard unbuffered Unix file I/O functions (development)"
ldesc: "libgfileio is a C++ library that wraps around the standard unbuffered
Unix file I/O functions write() and read(). Besides those, it provides some
other wrappers around file related functions. It is type safe and extensively
uses C++ exceptions for error conditions."
